小心翼翼、提心吊胆，疫情下的电竞比赛开始逐渐复苏。
Cautiously and fearfully, the competition began to recover from the outbreak.
白衣沽酒。
Gun wine in white.
文化。
Culture.
电竞行业损失难以估量的一年。
Atletico industry losses inestimable year.
。
.
3月9日，玩家们打开《英雄联盟》职业联赛春季赛直播间，看到两位带着硕大而显眼的口罩的解说。
On March 9, players opened the Heroes League spring game studio and saw two men wearing large, visible masks.
。
.
“让我猜猜，这是记得和猫哥。
"Let me guess, this is remember with Cat Brother.
”弹幕里玩家们这样调侃着。
Players in the canister are making fun of it.
。
.
作为国内最受瞩目的电竞赛事之一，LPL春季赛第二周的比赛，经历了漫长的休赛期后，终于在3月9日这一天于线上拉开了帷幕。
The second week of the spring LPL, one of the country's most watched TV competitions, was finally kicked off on March 9 after a long recess.
。
.
此时全球《英雄联盟》职业联赛都笼罩在疫情的阴影下，欧洲联赛将总决赛场地从布达佩斯更换到柏林，日本方面采用无观众的空场比赛模式，新建立的太平洋赛区（简称PCS）不得不延迟开赛。
The world's Heroes league is now overshadowed by an epidemic, with the European League shifting its Finals from Budapest to Berlin, Japan adopting spectator-free play mode and the newly established Pacific Rim (PCS) having to delay the start of the tournament.
疫情严重的韩国，在经历了主持人疑似感染的有惊无险后，随着疫情发展还是宣布了休赛。
South Korea, where the epidemic is severe, announced a break after suffering a suspected infection by a host.
。
.
而昨天LPL的比赛过程中，无论是解说还是接受采访的选手，都没有在镜头前露出正脸。
In the course of yesterday's LPL game, neither the commentator nor the interviewee showed his face in front of the camera.
解说则在比赛开始前向怀着担忧的观众透露，目前在演播室里的工作人员都佩戴了口罩，演播室也进行了全方位消毒。
The commentary was leaked to worried viewers before the start of the match, the studio staff were wearing masks, and the studio was thoroughly disinfected.
所有人都在努力向观众传达一个信息：疫情没有过去。
Everyone is trying to send a message to the audience that the epidemic is not over.
。
.
整个比赛过程相比从前省略了许多环节，LPL比赛节奏看上去加快了不少，过程似乎也变简单了。
The LPL's tempo seems to have quickened, and the process seems to have become simpler, with many links omitted from the game.
。
.
当然这背后情况并非如此简单。
This, of course, is not so simple.
在线上赛计划实行前，LPL官方一再和各个俱乐部强调，所有身在俱乐部的选手，必须在完成俱乐部隔离情况下，前往经过安全消毒的基地进行比赛。
Prior to the launch of the online playoff, LPL officials repeatedly and clubs stressed that all players in the club must travel to a safe disinfection base to compete in the event of the completion of the club isolation.
。
.
为了保证线上比赛能够顺利进行，LPL官方在2月26日-29日进行了线上公开训练赛，对训练地点网络进行了测评。
To ensure that the online competition can proceed smoothly, LPL officials conducted an online public training competition from February 26 to 29 to evaluate the network of training venues.
同时为了保证比赛公正性，官方还派出指定人员前往比赛地点进行监管。
In order to ensure the impartiality of the game, officials also sent designated personnel to the race site for supervision.
而如果需要从上海前往外地俱乐部，指定人员还需要提前前往该地区并隔离14天。
If travel from Shanghai to a foreign club is required, the designated person will also need to travel to the area early and remain in isolation for 14 days.
。
.
作为较早复工的行业，LPL线上开赛受到了一些电视台的关注，他们对相关人员进行了报道，并做了采访。
The early resumption of the industry, the LPL online games received some television attention, they reported on the relevant personnel, and gave interviews.
接受采访的拳头游戏中国负责人在电视直播中透露，“我们从2月初就已经开始做准备了。
"We've been making preparations since early February," China's head of the fist game was quoted live on television.
”。
"
为了弥补过去一个多月失去的赛程时间，LPL赛程将原本六天一休的比赛日程改为七天，并为大部分比赛日增加了比赛，希望能赶在季中赛之前完成赛程。
To make up for lost schedule over the past month, the LPL has changed its six-day schedule to seven days and added races for most of the day, hoping to finish ahead of the midseason.
。
.
近期上海发布了《上海市促进文化创意产业发展财政扶持资金申报指南》，其中明确指出对演艺、文旅、电竞、文化会展等受疫情影响较大、主动创新转型、信用良好、符合条件的中小微文创企业，优先予以支持。
Shanghai recently issued the "Guide to Reporting Financial Support Funds for Promoting the Development of Cultural and Creative Industries," which clearly indicates that priority should be given to small and medium-sized micro-enterprises affected by the epidemic, such as performing arts, cultural tourism, power stations, cultural exhibitions, etc.
从某种意义上讲，上海地区对于特殊期间的电竞产业给予了相当的优待。
In a sense, Shanghai has given considerable preferential treatment to the special period of the ECG industry.
。
.
但是准备充分也不能保证万事无忧，季中赛日期推迟，洲际赛情况不明，在中国以外，疫情还影响着其他赛区，电竞行业在这场疫情下，也是一番人间百态。
But good preparation is no guarantee, the midseason date is delayed, the intercontinental situation is unclear, outside China, the epidemic is affecting other competition areas, the Atletico industry in this epidemic, is also a world situation.
。
.
空场。
Empty field.
欧洲疫情让足球五大联赛也受到了疫情影响，为了保证比赛进行，部分俱乐部不得已宣布空场进行比赛。
The epidemic in Europe has also affected the five major leagues, and some clubs have had to declare their matches vacant in order to keep the game going.
。
.
在他们之前，波兰卡托维兹的电竞比赛率先体验了一把特殊时期的空场。
Before them, the Polish Atletico competition in Katowice was the first to experience a special period of vacancy.
相信不少人都了解欧洲玩家对于CS:GO的狂热，但肺炎疫情的到来，给这场原本的电竞盛宴泼下一盆冷水。
I believe that many people understand the European players for CS: GO fanaticism, but the arrival of pneumonia, to the original ECG banquet poured cold water.
。
.
来自突尼斯的CS:GO狂热爱好者Mouadh，为即将到来的IEM卡托维兹CS:GO比赛感到兴奋，他在Reddit上发帖，“我做到了！经过多年对梦想的追寻，我现在距离Spodek只有130米！”Spodek Arena是IEM举办CS:GO常用场地，可容纳1万多人同时观赛，也是许多CS:GO玩家的朝圣之地。
CS: GO fanatic Mouadh from Tunis, excited about the upcoming IEM Katowice CS: GO contest, posted on Reddit, "I did it! After years of chasing dreams, I'm only 130 meters from Spodek!" Spodek Arena, a common site for more than 10,000 people to watch the CS: GO at the same time, is also a hajj for many CS: GO players.
。
.
然而这个帖子在被发出后不久，官方遭到了官方的“无情拒绝”。
But soon after the post was posted, officials were met with an official "callous refusal."
距离比赛还有18小时时，IEM官方声明，出于对观众健康情况的考虑，他们决定本届IEM卡托维兹将不对外开放。
With 18 hours to go, IEM officials said they decided the IEM Katowice session would be closed to the public because of concerns about the health of the audience.
。
.
Mouadh为了观看这场比赛筹划数年，如今疫情带来的坏消息打破了他所有的计划。
Mouadh has been planning to watch the game for years, and now the bad news from the outbreak is upsetting all his plans.
这个帖子一度被推到Reddit首页，数万条回复中，网友们对这位狂热玩家的遭遇表示了同情。
The post was once pushed to the Reddit home page, and in tens of thousands of responses, netizens expressed sympathy for the fanatic.
。
.
事后接受媒体采访的CARMAC。
CARMAC interviewed by the media after the fact.
IEM卡托维兹的组织者CARMAC得知这件事后，特意为Mouadh安排了一场见面会。
When CARMAC, the organizer of IEM Katowice, learned of the incident, he arranged a meeting for Mouadh.
。
.
CARMAC比Mouadh更郁闷。
CARMAC is even more depressing than Mouadh.
在2月，疫情在欧洲没有像今天这样蔓延的时候，他们曾得到场馆方面的多次保证，比赛可以顺利进行。
In February, when the epidemic did not spread as it does today in Europe, they received assurances from the stadium that the game would go smoothly.
当然IEM组织方并没有懈怠，他们从2月起就关注着事件发展，也为此多次开会商讨疫情影响和必要措施。
The IEM organizers, of course, have not relented; they have been following events since February, and have met several times to discuss the impact of the outbreak and the necessary measures.
。
.
以往气氛火热的卡托维兹CS:GO比赛现场。
The atmosphere of the past heat of the Katowice CS: GO game scene.
然而最不理想的情况还是发生了，在比赛开始前几个小时，政府吊销了他们的大型赛事举办许可。
The worst of it happened, however, when, hours before the start of the race, the government revoked their big-ticket approvals.
。
.
CARMAC和他的同事最终争取到了在空场进行比赛的结果，并很无奈的公布了消息。
CARMAC and his colleagues eventually managed to win the result of the game in the open field and announced the news in frustration.
好在观众们很给力，比赛期间，数据显示Steam上的CS:GO玩家接近100万，创下历史记录，同时直播平台情况也十分可观。
Fortunately for the audience, during the game, the data showed a record number of CS: GO players on Steam, close to a million, and the live broadcast platform was impressive.
在这空场进行的欧洲电竞盛事因为线上观众的支持倒也没有显得尴尬。
The European Atletico event in the void was not embarrassed by the support of the online audience.
。
.
2020年的卡托维兹Spodek体育馆。
Katowice Spodek Stadium in 2020.
经历过一次这种情形的CARMAC，对自己团队接下来要在洛杉矶举办的Dota2赛事，以及即将在巴西举办的CS:GO赛事表示担忧。
CARMAC, which has experienced this once, is concerned about its team's upcoming Dota2 event in Los Angeles, as well as the upcoming CS: GO tournament in Brazil.
。
.
“如果举办一个公众活动，参与者不再安全，那显然不是进行比赛的合适时机。
"If there is a public event and the participants are no longer safe, it's obviously not the right time to play.
你得保证所有人健康，这才是最重要的。
You have to keep everyone healthy. That's the most important thing.
”。
"
延后。
Delayed.
疫情打乱了CARMAC的计划，更打乱了《守望先锋联赛》（以下简称OWL）的计划。
The outbreak disrupted CARMAC's plans and disrupted plans for the Wingguard Pioneer League (OWL).
经过两个赛季后，暴雪官方决定在2020年，初步实现在全球各个主队的主场城市进行比赛的计划。
After two seasons, Blizzard's official decision is to start playing in the home cities of home teams around the world by 2020.
如果成功，OWL则将会是第一个真正做到全球地域化的电竞赛事。
If it succeeds, OWL will be the first truly global geographies.
。
.
然而随着武汉封城，国内疫情逐步焦灼，暴雪取消了原本在杭州、广州、上海的主场比赛，原本被热情粉丝抢购一空的比赛门票，不得不草草作废。
However, with the closure of Wuhan, the domestic epidemic gradually worried, Blizzard cancelled the original home game in Hangzhou, Guangzhou, Shanghai, the original fans rushed to buy out tickets, had to be hastily canceled.
这还不是最难的，国内疫情逐渐稳定后，韩国却一夜间成为中国之外疫情最严重的国家，OWL赛事方又不得不放弃了首尔王朝队主场。
That's not the hardest part. After the epidemic stabilized, South Korea became the worst country outside China overnight, and OWL players had to give up the home court of the Seoul dynasty.
一时间太平洋赛区五支战队也纷纷“沦陷”，只能眼巴巴的看着OWL第三赛季在大洋另一边如期举行。
For a while the five Pacific Regional Clan also "fell", can only watch the OWL third season on the other side of the ocean as scheduled.
。
.
看到隔壁LPL已经线上开赛的粉丝们，一时难掩羡慕之情。
Seeing fans of the LPL next door already online, it's hard to help feeling envious for a moment.
。
.
如今，北美及欧洲情形愈发不明朗，包括OWL在内的海外电竞赛事方如今个个提心吊胆，如同等待“审判”。
Today, the situation in North America and Europe is increasingly uncertain, with overseas players, including OWL, now waiting for a "trial."
。
.
根据新闻数据，中国电竞行业在这段停滞的时间内，延期赛事超过500多场，直接经济损失超过10亿，必须复工则是国内电竞赛事不得不面对的现实。
According to news data, China's Atletico industry in this period of stagnation, more than 500 postponed events, direct economic losses of more than 1 billion, had to resume work is a domestic electricity competition had to face the reality.
。
.
接下来的几周内，在国内包括《王者荣耀》在内的多款热门电竞比赛，也将以线上形式进行。
In the next few weeks, several hotly contested domestic competitions, including "The Glory of the King," will also be held online.
原本花费多年终于脱离线上，脱离小网吧，努力走到线下的中国电竞，如今似乎又回到了从前。
Originally spent many years to finally leave the line, leaving the small Internet cafes, efforts to reach the online Chinese Atletico, now seems to return to the past.
。
.
2020年，所有人都等待着烟消云散的那天，等待雨后彩虹的降临。
In 2020, everyone waits for the day when the smoke clears and the rainbow comes after the rain.
。
.
